EXPECTED OUTCOME

Phase-9 will not necessarily increase recovery counts.

Instead it will reveal:

- which truth layers survive most often
- when recovery downgrades from named to anonymous
- when ordered recovery becomes unordered
- how metadata placement strategies perform

These results inform future format design decisions.

